	measure Value_by_Product_Actual = ```
			
			var _date  =  DATE( 2025, 01, 01)  --EDATE( today() , -2 )
			
			RETURN
			SUMX(
			    FILTER(
			        'SnapShot by Product', 
			        'SnapShot by Product'[Period / Set of Books] = "Actual / Current Forecast"
			        --&& 'Results by Product'[Date] <= DATE( YEAR(_date), MONTH(_date), 1 )
			    ),   
			    [Value_by_Product] 
			)
			```
